    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><strong>《蔓不生长》就像一本唯美的画册，一首令人心神宁静的乐曲，讲述一位与众不同的少年，为了寻找特别之处的真相，踏上冒险的旅途。唯有你的智慧，能协助他探究世界未知的真相。</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >▼ 探索「植化」的真相</h2><br>自古以来流传的植化，成年后身上的枝桠会急遽生长变成植物，传说中只要抵达淨土另一端，就能找到了解「植化」的真相。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860900/extras/3e62ed8a201aeb3602dba5108b0872e2.avif?t=1743409024\" width=600 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >▼ 翻转视角，水平思考</h2><br>看似单纯的拖曳与点击，透过视角的转换，将为场景带来不可思议的惊人变化。 《蔓不生长》的核心机制就是「转换视角」，透过镜头角度的转换以解开各种障碍与谜题，突破盲点，改变思维，享受水平思考的乐趣。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860900/extras/41e7b6144c1cc724206471573a344480.poster.avif?t=1743409024\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860900/extras/41e7b6144c1cc724206471573a344480.webm?t=1743409024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860900/extras/41e7b6144c1cc724206471573a344480.mp4?t=1743409024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860900/extras/9ecf7387a869e0ddfc6e7567dbadfacc.poster.avif?t=1743409024\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860900/extras/9ecf7387a869e0ddfc6e7567dbadfacc.webm?t=1743409024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860900/extras/9ecf7387a869e0ddfc6e7567dbadfacc.mp4?t=1743409024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >▼ 寻找自我的唯美童话</h2><br>「我是谁？」「我为何不一样？」<br>在本作中你能以轻松愉快的步调享受解谜的过程，与旅途结识的女孩携手克服难关。在疗愈动人的配乐下，沉浸在绿意盎然的世界里，一同找寻人生大哉问的解答。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860900/extras/fcecf7571976c2a1e352bfe83670a2ed.avif?t=1743409024\" width=600 height=200 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >▼ 荣获多项肯定</h2><br>《蔓不生长》荣获「放视大赏行动游戏创作金奖」、「青春设计节互动科技与游戏设计类金奖」、巴哈姆特 ACG 创作大赛优选」、「放视大赏雷亚游戏特别赏」及「K.T.科艺奖金奖」等多项殊荣。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860900/extras/de730488a38f40b48da2a83fe2e633dd.avif?t=1743409024\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br><strong>究竟在前方等待少年的命运与真相是什么？<br>邀请你一起踏上寻觅自我的绝美旅程。</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
